<h2 id="why-desktop">Why the desktop app?</h2>

<p>The web app at <a href="/">convertflow.live</a> already does everything. The desktop app exists for users who want:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Native file system access</strong> — drag a 500 MB JSONL from the file explorer, no upload step.</li>
  <li><strong>Offline use</strong> — once installed, no internet needed (HuggingFace pushes still go over the network when you trigger them).</li>
  <li><strong>Larger local storage</strong> — no localStorage 5–10 MB quota; the desktop app can persist more state.</li>
  <li><strong>System integration</strong> — pinned to taskbar / dock, opens via file association, system tray (coming soon).</li>
  <li><strong>The "real app" feel</strong> — its own window, command-Q to quit, native menu bar.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="web-version">Or use it in the browser</h2>

<p>
  No download required. Open <a href="/">convertflow.live</a> in any modern browser — same UI, same features, same 100%-local processing.
  Bookmark it or "install" it as a PWA from the browser address bar if you want it pinned without a real download.
</p>

<h2 id="verify">Verify your download</h2>

<p>
  Each release is built from <a href="https://github.com/abhijathk/convertFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">the public GitHub repo</a> via a reproducible CI workflow (<code>.github/workflows/desktop-release.yml</code>).
  SHA-256 checksums are published in the GitHub release page alongside the binaries.
</p>

<p>
  Once signed (Windows EV cert + macOS notarization), installers will not trigger SmartScreen/Gatekeeper warnings.
  Until then, you may see "unidentified developer" — right-click → Open (macOS) or "More info" → "Run anyway" (Windows).
</p>

</DocLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Download grid ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .download-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 20px 0 16px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 760px) {
    .download-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .download-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  /* ── Card shell ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .download-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 14px 16px;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 18px 18px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.12s, box-shadow 0.12s;
  }
  .download-card:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 50%, var(--border));
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px -8px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 30%, transparent);
  }

  /* ── Icon column ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .dl-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 8%, transparent);
  }
  .dl-icon.ubuntu {
    color: inherit;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 4px;
  }

  /* ── Body column ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .dl-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .dl-platform {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .dl-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── Action buttons (primary + secondary side by side) ──────────────── */
  .dl-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .dl-btn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
    transition: background 0.1s, border-color 0.1s, color 0.1s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  .dl-btn-label {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .dl-btn-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    opacity: 0.75;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .dl-btn.primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
  }
  .dl-btn.primary:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 88%, white);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .dl-btn.secondary {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: var(--border);
    color: var(--ink-dim);
  }
  .dl-btn.secondary:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 50%, var(--border));
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* ── Footer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .dl-foot {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .dl-foot a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .dl-foot a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
